a leader in the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742613-why-crowdstrike-still-has-more-room-to-run", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:30:19"}, {"id": "4742627", "title": "November Jobs Report: A Return To Normalcy Following Flat October", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business colleagues meeting in modern conference room\" data-id=\"2155192216\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">MoMo Productions</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The November jobs report reflected a return to normalcy following an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4732009-october-jobs-report-hurricanes-and-strike-activity-spook-payroll-growth\">October readout</a> that showed job gains as essentially flat from the month prior. As one of the final major datapoints ahead of the upcoming Federal Open Market Committee (\"FOMC\") meeting, the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742627-november-jobs-report-a-return-to-normalcy-following-flat-october", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:20:42"}, {"id": "4742446", "title": "ICL Group: Looking Beyond US Borders And Finding Value In Israel", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"USA &amp; Israeli Flags\" data-id=\"184315804\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DeniseBush/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I am stepping out briefly from my ardent risk-manager mantra. I usually cover dividend stocks, ETFs and macro strategy. And when I do write about more exciting market areas, it is usually along the lines of using a Magnificent 7 stock's volatility to earn</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742446-icl-group-looking-beyond-us-borders-finding-value-in-israel", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:00:00"}, {"id": "4742606", "title": "Procore: Future Remains Bright", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"House project in virtual reality\" data-id=\"1351472483\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Warchi</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>To summarize my investment thesis, when I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4682475-procore-technologies-a-promising-founder-led-company-with-large-opportunity\">initially reviewed</a> Procore Technologies (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PCOR\" title=\"Procore Technologies, Inc.\">PCOR</a></span>) I liked that this founder-led company was disrupting an industry in desperate need of new technology. Procore has been steadily growing revenue and gaining new customers</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742606-procore-future-remains-bright", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 16:52:58"}, {"id": "4742621", "title": "Columbia Limited Duration Credit Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173695076/image_173695076.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hourglass and dollar shadow\" data-id=\"173695076\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4368px\" height=\"2912px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173695076/image_173695076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173695076/image_173695076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173695076/image_173695076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173695076/image_173695076.jpg?io=getty-c